ound wave that freezes enemies around you in a radius of r units for t seconds.&#10;&#10;## Entrophic Shield&#10;Shields player for n damage. After damage is exceeded the shield breaks.&#10;&#10;## Purification&#10;Heals the player by n health and removes any existing negative buffs.&#10;&#10;## AT Field&#10;creates a ring of particles around the player that damages any enemy in range for an extended period of time.&#10;&#10;## Invisibility&#10;Prevents NPCs from seeing the player for a short amount of time&#10;&#10;## Heal&#10;Gives the player a set amount of health&#10;&#10;" wrapText="true">
